Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.30,0:21:15.57,ED_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1\fsp-2}滲んだまま、溶けてゆく
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.63,0:21:18.62,ED_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1\fsp-2}もう一度、迷わず
